Now if you've not heard that term before, it's not just about well-being, it's about your whole life being good.

9
00:00:42.000 --> 00:00:49.000
Flourishing is a psychological buzzword, a word or phrase that has become fashionable and is being used a lot.

10
00:00:49.000 --> 00:00:52.000
Especially on television and in newspapers.

11
00:00:52.000 --> 00:01:02.000
People who are flourishing feel good about all aspects of their life, including happiness, health, relationships and financial security.

12
00:01:02.000 --> 00:01:04.000
Do you feel you're flourishing, Georgie?

13
00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:11.000
Yeah, I think I'm quite lucky, actually. I really like my job. I have a good family and friends.

14
00:01:11.000 --> 00:01:14.000
Everything's going well. What about you, Phil?

15
00:01:14.000 --> 00:01:18.000
I think the same. I'm happy and I've got everything I need.

16
00:01:19.000 --> 00:01:23.000
In this episode, we'll hear about the global flourishing study.

17
